OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FNew figures show only 30% of areas
OL,7,Funder NHS England are meeting the
OL,8,Fproper standards for 24/7 children's
OL,9,Fpalliative care, ITV News
OL,10,FCorrespondent Rachel Younger reports
OL,12,FBorn with a heart condition and a rare
OL,13,Fgenetic disorder, Jaxson may only have
OL,14,Fmonths left to live.
OL,16,FWhile his parents hope their 17-month-
OL,17,Fold son will live for longer, they are
OL,18,Ftrying to treasure every moment they
OL,19,Fstill have together.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/17
