OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FThat time, however, is largely being
OL,7,Ftaken up by fighting the NHS for basic
OL,8,Fsupplies and for a community nurse to
OL,9,Fvisit their home to oversee the
OL,10,Ftoddler's needs.
OL,12,F"We were told in September that
OL,13,Fcurative treatment would stop, and
OL,14,Fthat he would be placed on a
OL,15,Fpalliative journey," said Jaxson's
OL,16,Ffather, Jim Cirkel.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
