OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,F"The truth is, we just don't know how
OL,7,Flong we will have with Jaxson. It
OL,8,Fcould be tomorrow, or he could live to
OL,9,F15. There is absolutely no way of
OL,10,Fknowing, and that is why every single
OL,11,Fminute is important to us.
OL,13,F"So, we spend every day giving him the
OL,14,Fbest possible life that we can. Which
OL,15,Fis why, when we face red tape and
OL,16,Fbureaucracy trying to access support
OL,17,For equipment, it can be incredibly
OL,18,Ffrustrating.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/17
