OL,6,F"I don't want to spend time emailing
OL,7,Fand calling people, I just want to be
OL,8,Fwith my son."
OL,10,FJim, from south east London, has told
OL,11,FITV News how he's spent six weeks
OL,12,Ffighting "various departments within
OL,13,Fthe NHS" to get syringes used to
OL,14,Fadminister Jaxson's oral medication.
OL,26,@pD@MO]
