OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FHe added that they "don't administer
OL,7,Fthe medicine as smoothly once they are
OL,8,Freused and that "this can exacerbate
OL,9,FJaxson's reflux".
OL,11,F"Sometimes it does feel like the
OL,12,Fsystem is ignoring Jackson, or perhaps
OL,13,Fthey've written him off, because he's
OL,14,Fgoing to die, so what's the point `
OL,15,Fthat sort of attitude," Jim said.
OL,17,F"We've had a lot of fights just to get
OL,18,Fsimple things organised for him."
