OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FAfter spending most of his first year
OL,7,Fin hospital, Jaxson was moved to
OL,8,Fpalliative care at home, after which
OL,9,Fhis parents hoped for regular visits
OL,10,Ffrom a dedicated community nurse.
OL,12,FFive months on, they are still waiting.
OL,14,FJaxson's family has shared their story
OL,15,Fas new figures from charity Together
OL,16,Ffor Short Lives shows that only 30% of
OL,17,Flocal areas in England are meeting the
OL,18,Frequired standard for 24/7 end of life
OL,19,Fcare for children at home.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/17
