OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FFor safe staffing levels to be met,
OL,7,F4,960 children's community nurses
OL,8,Fwould be working in England, compared
OL,9,Fto the 902 currently employed by the
OL,10,FNHS, Together for Short Lives warns.
OL,11,FIn Wales, an additional 208 are needed.
OL,13,FAs it launches its "Short Lives Can't
OL,14,FWait" campaign, Together for Short
OL,15,FLives is calling for the UK's
OL,16,Fgovernments, NHS bodies and local
OL,17,Fauthorities to take immediate action
OL,18,Ffor the UK's 99,000 seriously ill
OL,19,Fchildren and their families.
