OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,FAndy Fletcher, Together for Short
OL,7,FLives chief executive said: "It is
OL,8,Funacceptable that families of
OL,9,Fseriously ill children are not getting
OL,10,Fthe palliative and end of life care
OL,11,Fthey need because of where they live.
OL,12,FThis is care that is clearly set out
OL,13,Fin standards, guidance and even the
OL,14,Flaw.
OL,16,F"Time is short for seriously ill
OL,17,Fchildren and their families. They
OL,18,Fcannot wait months for the next
OL,19,Felection, the next spending review,
OL,20,Fthe next set of planning guidance.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
