OL,3,CParents fight to get terminally ill
OL,4,Ctoddler the palliative care he needs
OL,6,F"Our deepest sympathies are with the
OL,7,Ffamilies of seriously ill children and
OL,8,Fwe want everyone to have access to the
OL,9,Fhigh-quality, personalised palliative
OL,10,Fcare that can make all the difference
OL,11,Fat such a challenging time.
OL,13,F"That's why we require all local NHS
OL,14,Fintegrated care boards to commission
OL,15,Fend of life care services to meet
OL,16,Ftheir patients' needs.
