OL,6,F"We have made over #350 million
OL,7,Favailable to hospices since 2020 to
OL,8,Fsecure and increase additional NHS
OL,9,Fcapacity and enable hospital
OL,10,Fdischarge, ensuring hospices can
OL,11,Fcontinue to deliver care to those who
OL,12,Fneed it.
OL,14,F"NHS England has also confirmed that,
OL,15,Fin 2024/25, it will once again be
OL,16,Fproviding #25m of funding to
OL,17,Fchildren's hospices in England."
